{"tid":2241610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡總統巡視「樂山雷達站」--監控範圍幾乎含括全東亞","createTime":"2020-10-13T11:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T04:19:22.000Z","uid":337052,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e254a136d2294599f5ef2c454d01a3209021e345","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:59:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">訪樂山雷達站送麻辣鍋底慰國軍 總統：長程飛彈預警是重中之重</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/10/13 19:20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20201013/1152x768_20201013000105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20201013%2F1152x768_20201013000105.jpg&h=4d7c7008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總統蔡英文13日視導空軍防空暨飛彈指揮部，慰勉國軍辛勞與付出。（總統府提供）中央社記者葉素萍傳真 109年10月13日<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者葉素萍台北13日電）<span class=\"red\">總統蔡英文今天前往海拔2620公尺的樂山雷達站視導</span>，為體驗國軍弟兄姊妹的日常，蔡總統選擇坐車上山，從山下到山上單趟車程就要兩小時，她兼當一日外送員，親自外送麻辣鍋底加菜；她說，長程飛彈的預警是國防任務重中之重。<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統今天視導空軍偵蒐預警中心（樂山雷達站）及空軍防空連。<br />\n<br />\n國安幕僚指出，蔡總統今天前往樂山雷達站，視察守衛樂山雷達站的防空連，「具有重要的戰略意義」。<span class=\"red\">樂山雷達站所監控的範圍，幾乎含括東北亞至東南亞地區</span>，特別在近期一段時間，中國的軍事行動頻頻，樂山雷達站的工作，就是精準掌握導彈及衛星等各項空中訊息，進行精準預判，並即時給予各單位最迅速的情資，讓各單位能夠迅速應變。<br />\n<br />\n國安幕僚表示，蔡總統因此特別安排前往視導，勉勵堅守崗位的國軍弟兄姊妹，也再次用具體行動回應日前國慶演說所提的，只要有時間，總統都會盡量前往部隊，看看日夜輪班、保家衛國的弟兄姊妹，從山上到海邊的單位，都沒有例外。<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統致詞時提到，她選擇一路坐車上山，就是為了要體驗大家的日常，從山下到山上車程就要兩小時，路途遙遠、山路也很崎嶇，想到大家每次輪休往返都要經歷這樣的車程，真的不容易，高山氣溫變化大，物資運補成本也一定很高，大家都辛苦了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/posts/10157064558291065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftsaiingwen%2Fposts%2F10157064558291065&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=dc966ccf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/posts/10157064558291065</a><br />\n<br />\n她說，要感謝大家在這座高山上當空防的眼睛，從台灣看到世界，從世界看到外太空，默默守護台灣的國家安全。她身為三軍統帥除了要代表國人幫大家打氣，也要讓所有國人了解，有一群弟兄姊妹在高山上全天候堅守著崗位，承擔偵蒐預警的重要任務。<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統說，她實際了解大家工作內容，看到大家在短時期內確實掌握了飛彈的軌跡並且迅速應變的專業能力，非常值得肯定；透過簡報，她也知道最近周邊國家試射飛彈、火箭，空軍偵蒐預警中心都能在第一時間確實偵獲，她很有信心大家一定會為其他專責反制的國軍單位取得先機，成功抵禦來自空中的威脅，尤其長程飛彈的預警，更是國防任務的重中之重，「國家的空防就要繼續交給各位了」。<br />\n<br />\n她說，山上天氣冷，補給路途也很遙遠，她給大家帶來麻辣鍋，因為來不及準備，所以大家今天中午吃不到，但是找個時間好好享用她帶的麻辣鍋，這幾天可以加菜，大家都辛苦了、繼續努力。 （編輯：林興盟）1091013<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202010130162.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202010130162.aspx&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=9e2ae4fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202010130162.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"63c497e2476e35711e346527e28c2ee7e3d267e6","tid":2241610,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da859e83ea352045d8c75cc2a8df5f957f943e2e","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:02:22.000Z","msg":"中國敢動武&hellip;為了保護台灣的「它」 他曝美國必幫忙反擊<br />\n2019/01/20 16:08:00<br />\n追蹤三立：<br />\n<br />\n政治中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n中共領導人習近平在年初表示不排除武力攻台，若是真的侵台，美國會如何行動，也引發各界關注。對此，桃園市議員王浩宇也直言，<span class=\"red\">若是中共攻台，美國一定會出手，原因就是因為台灣有先進的雷達基地，若是落入中共手中，美國損失恐怕難以估計。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/20/1745250-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F20%2F1745250-XXL.jpg&h=b04f0d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ▲美國生產的鋪路爪長程預警雷達，台灣也有。（示意圖／翻攝自維基百科）<br />\n<br />\n王浩宇在臉書表示，經過這兩年的努力，台灣已經正式加入美日韓聯盟，劃入沖繩美軍防禦的區域，美軍除了與台灣共用軍事資訊、合作協防，更將亞洲最先進的AN/ FPS-115 PAVE PAWS SRP雷達設在台灣，作為美軍的前線預警。<br />\n<br />\n王浩宇進一步指出，<span class=\"red\">SRP雷達最遠可以看到哈爾濱、新疆、北韓，超過3千公里的範圍，任何飛彈或武器只要移動，就會被美軍掌握，同時相關資訊也會分享給台灣。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">「這個雷達基地如果不慎落入中共，美國的損失恐怕難以估計！」</span>王浩宇直言，若是中國對台灣動武，美國不會坐視不管，一定會打回去，要大家絕對別懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n由美商雷神公司（Raytheon Company）生產的鋪路爪長程預警雷達（PAVE PAWS），位在新竹五峰鄉與苗栗泰安鄉交界的樂山雷達站，隸屬於空軍作戰指揮部，可提供遠程飛彈預警。值得一提的是，<span class=\"red\">2012年12月，北韓發射火箭引發國際關注，當時我國全程掌握發射到墜海過程，還比日本偵測快2分鐘，全是仰賴鋪路爪雷達。</span>（編輯：廖俐惠）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=487974&amp;fb_comment_id=2182897948422792_2183043068408280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D487974%26fb_comment_id%3D2182897948422792_2183043068408280&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=c9886f69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D487974%26fb_comment_id%3D2182897948422792_2183043068408280&h=025cdbd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=487974&amp;fb_comment_id=2182897948422792_2183043068408280</a>"},{"pid":"0ba39943222d8e0caffc835cfd871adc82266ed4","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c497e2476e35711e346527e28c2ee7e3d267e6","tid":2241610,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74388ced52a9b78aef842f2a8106f5cc48fff9f5","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/201812/mobile01-d2fd4e3c9b2c187a57fbdedcaba5f2e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2Fattach%2F201812%2Fmobile01-d2fd4e3c9b2c187a57fbdedcaba5f2e8.jpg&h=e9a70231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/174/d174392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F174%2Fd174392.jpg&h=2108c5e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e99dc0ced5e5bc7da95d28702bf7891dfc132e8e","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/27/2742127-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F27%2F2742127-PH.jpg&h=42c8e365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/27/2742129-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F27%2F2742129-PH.jpg&h=10bec863&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23998343a1a78f825d718d0e7cb9a71b921ab043","tid":2241610,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ba39943222d8e0caffc835cfd871adc82266ed4","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c497e2476e35711e346527e28c2ee7e3d267e6","tid":2241610,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"你每天看的新聞真多！"},{"pid":"6d5323914098222296085ab31a0bae54de848d23","tid":2241610,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"根本就係美軍既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9acecd2ae19785f1360db733661c0220f415c5d","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23998343a1a78f825d718d0e7cb9a71b921ab043","tid":2241610,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ba39943222d8e0caffc835cfd871adc82266ed4","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c497e2476e35711e346527e28c2ee7e