quote":{"pid":"76cdfb3dc30f3dc9da9f02b760d7de6c4905c985","tid":2241610,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"邊有美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aUYzAKSl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaUYzAKSl.jpg&h=7522a58c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:12:35.000Z","msg":"套野由雷神同LMT做main.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30dfb431685c04c5671948fb8574956776a5614","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:13:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">因應共機頻繁軍事活動 長程預警雷達加裝敵我識別器</span></strong><br />\n2020-09-10 17:29 聯合報 / 記者洪哲政／台北即時報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/09/10/realtime/8517745.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F09%2F10%2Frealtime%2F8517745.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=ea2146b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n空軍委託中科院，明年為部署樂山的偵蒐雷達（SRP，如圖）研發「偵蒐雷達計畫敵我識別裝備」，加裝於長程預警雷達運用，強化國軍所需台海當面「戰術情報」偵蒐。圖／國防部青年日報<br />\n<br />\n空軍樂山偵蒐雷達（SRP）明年（110）將支出高達24億1434萬元，用以執行「偵蒐雷達後續維持」，<span class=\"red\">空軍同時委託中科院，為偵蒐雷達進行附屬設施維護，且考量共機在當面活動頻繁，因此自行編列預算，委由中科院研發「偵蒐雷達計畫敵我識別裝備」，加裝於長程預警雷達運用，強化「戰術情報」偵蒐。</span><br />\n<br />\n國防部送交立法院的109年中共軍力報告書表示，近期美軍聯合盟邦擴大在東海、台海及南海地區機艦巡弋力度，中共調整沿海當面機場增駐多型新式空中兵力，以應對美籍機艦高強度、大範圍抵近偵察與常態自由航行作為；今年6月起，共機多次藉由應對美機之際進入我西南防空識別區，軍事部署與活動重點，已漸次由我西部當面地區向西南延伸。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">長程預警雷達在民國102年1月31日擔負戰備，依我方要求，能360度偵追3300公里內，南至南海、北至南北韓空域內，包括戰術彈道飛彈、各類飛機航空器目標，且能偵獲200公里內低雷達截面積的巡弋飛彈、無人飛行載具等目標，現已完成與北部、東部兩座飛彈預警中心連線。</span><br />\n<br />\n但美方與我「合作」部署長程預警雷達，主要是執行美方對各國包括大陸在內「戰略情報」偵蒐任務，所以有大批美方技術代表駐防樂山執勤，情報直接由美方掌握；國軍所需當面台海空域「戰術情報」，如共機出海後在台海當面的情態掌握與辨識判讀，才是國軍當下最需要的資。由於我方發現共機多機出海後，發展出只由單一指揮戰機開啟雷達與詢答器，其他戰機均關閉候令，以此造成識別混淆的戰術，因此「自掏腰包」委中科院為雷達系統研發敵我識別器，強化判讀，滿足空軍的「戰術情報」需求。<br />\n<br />\n川普政府是在2017年售我樂山雷達站「SRP偵蒐雷達」後續維持案，當時外界推測這項軍購約為12億3310萬元。但國防部110年度預算案記載，「偵蒐雷達後續維持」軍購案，110年度計需對美匯出美金8034萬4093美元，合計達新台幣24億1434萬元。此外，「偵蒐雷達附屬設施維護」委製案，也由中科院承製，計需1億4711萬5千元；「偵蒐雷達計畫敵我識別裝備」委製案同樣由中科院執行，計需500萬元，都納入110年度執行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4850211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F4850211&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=3355c764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4850211</a>"},{"pid":"d7a3b8fd43fa9bd7282bc8df4cb8f95346392877","tid":2241610,"uid":294182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"鋪路爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805b43e2eb5353c9159cba9f4cbab22386dde9bd","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"76cdfb3dc30f3dc9da9f02b760d7de6c4905c985","tid":2241610,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"邊有美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aUYzAKSl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaUYzAKSl.jpg&h=7522a58c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2020/10/1602582489999-694f4439c0b441c9a02221330abcf36c-800x466.jpg?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2020%2F10%2F1602582489999-694f4439c0b441c9a02221330abcf36c-800x466.jpg%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=2baaef90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蔡英文總統於13日前往樂山雷達站，視導「空軍偵蒐預警中心」及「空軍防空連」，行程中卻出現一名未穿軍服的神秘外籍男子，耐人尋味。（圖／軍聞社提供）"},{"pid":"b8249f7ff6ef8ed9e60e692e0eae89b8884158f8","tid":2241610,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"個雷達站有撚用咩, 一開戰第一時間被摧毀."},{"pid":"0c6cb2075ee0c648f984457608037a5c11c09289","tid":2241610,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"我喺香港打j小英係咪都會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff4af00e8ffbeb48980c027fad608256ac632c1","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8249f7ff6ef8ed9e60e692e0eae89b8884158f8","tid":2241610,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"個雷達站有撚用咩, 一開戰第一時間被摧毀."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:16:30.000Z","msg":"「樂山雷達站」四周都是防空飛彈"},{"pid":"41611f532f0a0921672a444b167f0d03c0612f36","tid":2241610,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"同場加映<br />\n雜種睇片閱兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Asw3fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Asw3fb.png&h=b83e0656&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33f55271c124914fef45fb4a9a8b2dc1bfce5e80","tid":2241610,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:18:02.000Z","msg":"台灣都開始扮都唔扮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d5a70803f93d6c53165b6f783dcb28653940d0","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41611f532f0a0921672a444b167f0d03c0612f36","tid":2241610,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2