tion Vehicle Entry（精準取得入境載具）的縮寫，為美國空軍對於電子系統的計劃代號；「PAWS」是Phased Array Warning System（相位陣列預警系統）的縮寫。雷神公司為雷達主承包商，並由IBM聯邦系統（現由洛克希德馬丁收購，為洛克希德‧馬丁系統整合公司）研發軟體。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edfb552566af4864f00439c7ea0a3572fd5acc7","tid":2241610,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0fb90de8d49385d7d7fcca799504785db6f440","tid":2241610,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"比起過去舊型預警雷達，只能監控地面或水面發射的洲際彈道飛彈，雷神公司為中華民國設計的這型偵蒐雷達功能已加強為<span class=\"red\">可監控長、短程戰術彈道飛彈、巡航導彈及空中飛行目標等</span>，由於部署在高山上，雷達還<span class=\"red\">可俯視水面艦艇</span>。"},{"pid":"b04a235a631fc7a880fdfb5ac7b2eabefe884f64","tid":2241610,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"violet\">唔知呢個雷達睇唔睇到12人送中位置</span><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">五千幾公里應該有可能睇到</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">求專家研究下,麻煩跟進</span>"},{"pid":"2c9716864f2c29e801f4e4f78356aed7f3f3f528","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3405160e291c9acfe1fe6aec66098c09e33907f0","tid":2241610,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ff4af00e8ffbeb48980c027fad608256ac632c1","tid":2241610,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8249f7ff6ef8ed9e60e692e0eae89b8884158f8","tid":2241610,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"個雷達站有撚用咩, 一開戰第一時間被摧毀."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:16:30.000Z","msg":"「樂山雷達站」四周都是防空飛彈"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:33:51.000Z","msg":"冇用, 大陸d多管火箭炮可以射200km, 有d重可以400km, 唔